{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289740/extras/descGif1_v3.gif?t=1733743025\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289740/extras/text_3.png?t=1733743025\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to the world of Power Sink, our friend the Diver is one of many occupants in a gorgeous underwater colony, full of familiar life and buzzing with energy. Well... at least it was. Something's gone wrong and it's your job to venture into the depths of your home to restore the connections between your community and the well forgotten about power station that lies below. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You must traverse the aging structures beneath you, reconnect a series of Station Platforms and piece together the cause of the <i><strong>explosive</strong></i> depowering of the world around. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore and repair the station before your home falls into ruin.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289740/extras/descGif2_v3.gif?t=1733743025\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289740/extras/text_2.png?t=1733743025\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Logic-based Circuitry Puzzles</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play with plenty of interesting circuit components, to power your way around, solve a conundrum or simply light up your world</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Classic Platforming Goodness</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Run and Jump with the best of them. The Diver's abilities are simple yet satisfying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Diverse Aquatic Atmospheres</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into the vast oceanic void before you. The secrets of the station await.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Immersive Soundscape &amp; Original Tunes</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The world around is brought to life by the creaks &amp; groans of the station along with a variety of specially crafted tracks for your puzzling pleasure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289740/extras/descGif3_v3.gif?t=1733743025\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289740/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733743025","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289740/page.bg.jpg?t=1733743025","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289740/0c8a3d47260c90661be4792c1f328a2504cec0c0/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733743025","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289740/0c8a3d47260c90661be4792c1f328a2504cec0c0/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733743025","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"HDR available","id":61}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2408100,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>JOIN OUR COMMUNITY</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289740/extras/ezgif-5-ee6ec2b239.gif?t=1733743025\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289740/extras/discordLink.png?t=1733743025\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb